trans-unit.source: Publishes authenticated, encrypted SOAP virtual roots on servers.
trans-unit.target: Publiserer godkjente, kryptert SOAP virtuelle rotmapper på serverne.

trans-unit.source: See <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.SoapServerVRoot> for the default implementation.
trans-unit.target: Se <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.SoapServerVRoot>for standard implementering.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.SoapServerVRoot>

trans-unit.source: ISoapServerVRoot is used internally by the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: ISoapServerVRoot er brukt internt av .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: You do not need to use it directly in your code.
trans-unit.target: Du trenger ikke å bruke den direkte i koden.

trans-unit.source: Creates a SOAP virtual root with security options.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en virtuell rotmappe for SOAP med sikkerhetsalternativer.
